caption.p: Chemical compositions of the leaf essential oils of Litsea viridis, Machilus balansae, Machilus grandifolia, Neolitsea ellipsoidea, and Phoebe angustifolia collected in Vietnam.

fn.p: RI calc = Retention index determined with respect to a homologous series of n-alkanes on a HP-5ms column, RI db = Retention index from the databases [ 35, 36, 37], L.v. = Litsea viridis, M.b. = Machilus balansae, M.g. = Machilus grandifolia, N.e. = Neolitsea ellisoidea, P.a. = Phoebe angustifolia.
